flowchart TD
  A[Start: LIFF or Web open] --> B[Load /api/config]
  B --> C{LIFF_ID exists?}
  C -- yes --> D[liff.init]
  C -- no --> E[Web demo mode]
  D --> F[note ID input]
  E --> F
  F --> G{Allowlisted?}
  G -- no --> H[Reject]
  G -- yes --> I[Session token]
  I --> J[Upload file + OCR helper text]
  J --> K[OCR adapter]
  K --> L[Extract land constraints]
  L --> M[Apply FAR / road width rule]
  M --> N[Estimate footprint, floor area, floors, units]
  N --> O[Create CSV / Excel / TXT]
  O --> P[Return result and download links]
